                            <comment id="16695065" author="tilman" created="Wed, 21 Nov 2018 18:23:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The previous change introduced the bug you thankfully reported. I fixed this and also added a test. Until 2.0.13 is released you can try a snapshot:&lt;/p&gt;

